  "remarks": "Head of the KGB, former Head of the Investigation Committee, former Chief of the Operational and Analytical Center of the President's Administration, responsible for telecommunications, including monitoring, filtering, controlling and intervening different communication channels, for example the internet. As Head of the KGB, he is responsible for the repressive activity of the KGB against civil society and democratic opposition.",
